{"tid":1443000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先睇yt見到呢個藍絲channel賣廣告，話係外國勢力誤導年青人","createTime":"2019-08-11T06:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:43:23.000Z","uid":159523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"656f8c1175e208ca1d69143a1f15c73c5377c4e6","tid":1443000,"uid":159523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gBooWDBcXK0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgBooWDBcXK0&d=gk%2Bh3YXCSP8KuySO9FkCKnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=18c1b3b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gBooWDBcXK0</a><br />\n講真，以前真係當笑話睇<br />\n<br />\n點知尋日同個66歲既長輩食飯，佢同我講，最近去工聯會學電腦，上youtube就成日睇到黑衣人收外國人錢搞事 balala 仲叫我唔好同流合污<br />\n<br />\n佢係一個好仁慈既長者黎，但少少既洗腦msg已經可以令到佢地有偏見<br />\n<br />\n呢種片居然都可以讚多過負皮，仲植入埋yt 5秒廣告<br />\n雖然唔知負皮有冇用，但我覺得如果負皮多過正皮既應該會令可信度降低？<br />\n<br />\nBtw，呢種藍絲文宣已經入侵到yt 5秒廣告了<br />\n真係好多中年/老人家以為係有咩外國勢力，我地係咪可以效法下佢地係yt做多d文宣？"},{"pid":"ddc96c2a55994c96cd8a858434e2b5f4fd866b05","tid":1443000,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZbgh24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZbgh24.jpg&h=3a16159d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nV4d4Je.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnV4d4Je.jpg&h=fe1a6b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irD6Fgx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FirD6Fgx.jpg&h=8a341101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxQprWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxQprWy.jpg&h=523589e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQFs89L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQFs89L.jpg&h=e6ad67c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KomTkgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h